title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Bowl Special
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back with picks a bowl special. The last episode of the year had to go out with a bang including competing podcast drama, charity disputes and special guests. See you in 2021!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
